googleReviewsBySlug.json.name: Megan Marion
googleReviewsBySlug.json.text: Words cannot express how Thankful I am for Jared coming out to replace my 30 year old hot water heater. I explained to him that my water was not getting hot and I thought that I could repair it by taking out the old heating elements and putting in new ones well that didn't work as planned and I had an even bigger leak. I sent Jared a picture of my old water heater and from his experience he was able to tell me that my water heater had been leaking for quite a while and suggested that it was time to get a new one if I was ready. We set up an appointment and he brought a new electric water heater (better quality and more efficient then lows and Hm dept) and installed it. He made the proper fitting adjustments to my old pipes. He also helped me locate my water meter so that he could turn off the water it was covered in 2 inches of dirt and he dug it out. He is very professional and polite (ma'am). Don't hesitate to contact this company. You will be satisfied with the end result and finally have hot water. Don't wait!!!!
